msgstr "使用例は&lt;<chaining-kafka-transactions-with-hibernate-reactive-transactions>&gt;</chaining-kafka-transactions-with-hibernate-reactive-transactions>に記載されています<chaining-kafka-transactions-with-hibernate-reactive-transactions>。</chaining-kafka-transactions-with-hibernate-reactive-transactions>"

